      "author": "BiancaT (Bianca Taylor)",
      "cookedHtml": "<h1><a name=\"p-143488-new-feature-in-gradual-release-teams-assigned-as-owners-of-boards-and-docs-1\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-143488-new-feature-in-gradual-release-teams-assigned-as-owners-of-boards-and-docs-1\"></a><strong>New feature in gradual release: Teams assigned as owners of boards and docs <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/busts_in_silhouette.png?v=15\" title=\":busts_in_silhouette:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":busts_in_silhouette:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></strong></h1>\n<p>Teams will soon be able to be board owners of boards and docs, making board and doc management more clear, easy, and accessible.</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/6/d/6df67cb44c075f5ecec52bb09a4fd9ac1741a94e.png\" title=\"large-Screen Shot 2023-08-22 at 12.22.28 pm\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/6/d/6df67cb44c075f5ecec52bb09a4fd9ac1741a94e_2_563x500.png\" alt=\"large-Screen Shot 2023-08-22 at 12.22.28 pm\" width=\"563\" height=\"500\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">large-Screen Shot 2023-08-22 at 12.22.28 pm</span><span class=\"informations\">882×782 55.5 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<h3><a name=\"p-143488-this-new-improvement-also-means-that-in-situations-where-an-owner-is-no-longer-with-the-accountcompany-there-is-a-team-of-other-board-owners-there-to-save-the-day-2\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-143488-this-new-improvement-also-means-that-in-situations-where-an-owner-is-no-longer-with-the-accountcompany-there-is-a-team-of-other-board-owners-there-to-save-the-day-2\"></a>This new improvement also means that in situations where an owner is no longer with the account/company, there is a team of other board owners there to save the day <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/dizzy.png?v=15\" title=\":dizzy:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":dizzy:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></h3>\n<p>How do we feel about this update? <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/wink.png?v=15\" title=\":wink:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":wink:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/person_shrugging.png?v=15\" title=\":person_shrugging:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":person_shrugging:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>"
    },
    {
      "id": 144790,
      "postNumber": 2,
      "createdAt": "2023-09-21T04:57:15.729Z",
      "author": "IanHas (Ian Haselden)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>Thanks for this new feature it’s something our company will use.  Can adding Teams as Board Owners be included in the Create a board from template automation Advanced options.  Currently only individuals can be added in the automation.  Thanks<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/f/e/fe71cf0c684b0ed0d1be5f8bca7e5f692ae85735.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/f/e/fe71cf0c684b0ed0d1be5f8bca7e5f692ae85735_2_456x500.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"456\" height=\"500\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">518×567 28.2 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>"
    },
    {
