      "cookedHtml": "<p>Love this idea! I will take it with the product team and update you when I hear back <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/rocket.png?v=12\" title=\":rocket:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":rocket:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>"
