      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hey <a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/ianhas\">@IanHas</a> - thanks for your patience with me!</p>\n<p>In some exciting news, our team is currently working on this particular feature… stay tuned for updates in the near future <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/eyes.png?v=12\" title=\":eyes:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":eyes:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/star2.png?v=12\" title=\":star2:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":star2:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>"
